And next is this. Ta-da!

731
00:49:36,572 --> 00:49:41,572
姫森ルーナぬいぐるみ 守ってルーナイトver.
The Himemori Luna Plushie: Protect me LuKnight ver.!

732
00:50:00,080 --> 00:50:01,280
