831
00:55:51,138 --> 00:55:52,938
A. そこになければねのら！
A. If it's not there, then there's no reason!

832
00:56:04,838 --> 00:56:05,938
んなあああぁい！
Nnaaaaai!

833
00:56:06,138 --> 00:56:07,538
リピート アフター ミー
Repeat after me

834
00:56:08,138 --> 00:56:09,338
なんそい！！ なんそい！！
Nnasshoi!! Nnasshoi!!

835
00:56:09,638 --> 00:56:10,338
せーの
Ready, go!

836
00:56:10,638 --> 00:56:11,938
なんそい！！ なんそい！！
Nnasshoi!! Nnasshoi!!

837
00:56:12,238 --> 00:56:12,738
もう１回！
One more time!

838
00:56:12,838 --> 00:56:14,338
なんそい！！ なんそい！！
Nnasshoi!! Nnasshoi!!

839
00:56:15,238 --> 00:56:15,938
いいええ
Nice!

840
00:56:16,238 --> 00:56:17,938
熱い視線が集中
Hot gazes are focused

841
00:56:18,238 --> 00:56:20,638
ハラハラする心にムガムチュウ
Absorbed in the heart that flutters

842
00:56:21,138 --> 00:56:23,338
だから… だから…
Because... because...

843
00:56:23,838 --> 00:56:25,638
これでいいのら
This is fine

844
00:56:26,838 --> 00:56:29,438
泣きたい から笑いたい
I want to cry, so I want to laugh

845
00:56:29,938 --> 00:56:32,138
心だって奪ってあげるのら！
I'll steal your heart, you know!

846
00:56:32,538 --> 00:56:35,038
だから会いたい その願いに
Because I want to meet you, on that wish

847
00:56:35,538 --> 00:56:37,538
今 約束の合言葉
A promised password now

848
00:56:37,938 --> 00:56:39,938
いくよ！ なんそい！！
Let's go! Nnasshoi!!

849
00:56:40,438 --> 00:56:43,438
まどろみも ホラーな夜もあるけれど
Even the drowsy, scary nights exist, but

850
00:56:43,938 --> 00:56:45,738
でもね！ なんそい！！
But you know! Nnasshoi!!

851
00:56:46,138 --> 00:56:47,838
この先も みんな
Everyone, from here on too

852
00:56:48,138 --> 00:56:49,738
おりからへいき
It's okay to start over

853
00:56:50,138 --> 00:56:52,238
まだ遊び足りねぇのら！
I haven't played enough yet!

854
00:57:18,088 --> 00:57:21,088
出演
Cast

855
00:57:22,088 --> 00:57:24,588
姫森ルーナ
Himemori Luna

856
00:57:25,088 --> 00:57:27,588
尾丸ポルカ（ポル〜ナイト）
Omaru Polka (Polu~night)

857
00:57:28,088 --> 00:57:30,588
ルーナイト
Lu-Knight

858
00:59:40,088 --> 00:59:45,088
生誕ライブ見に来てくれてありがとうなのら...。
Thank you for coming to watch my birthday live...

859
00:59:45,088 --> 00:59:50,088
今年は体調不良の時期だったからまともに出せなかったかもしれない...。
Since I was feeling unwell this year, I might not have been able to give it my all...

860
00:59:50,088 --> 00:59:55,088
でも最後まで頑張ったのら！！ぷりいぬ！！
But I did my best until the end, even in Toy!! Puri-inu!!

861
00:59:55,088 --> 01:00:00,088
これからもずっとずっと姫様になる夢を応援してね！
Please keep supporting my dream of becoming a Princess forever!

862
01:00:00,088 --> 01:00:02,188
I love you ちゅぱちゅぱ... 2025.10.10 るーななのらー
I love you, chupa-chupa... 2025.10.10 It's Luna-nora~

863
01:00:05,096 --> 01:00:08,596
CH4NGE
Original: Giga / Cover: Amane Kanata

864
01:00:05,371 --> 01:00:06,596
とべ、起こせ！ 狙うは事故
Fly, make a move! Aiming for a crash

865
01:00:06,696 --> 01:00:08,296
一世一代さあ何賭す？
Once in a lifetime, come on, what will you bet?

866
01:00:08,496 --> 01:00:09,796
自問自答
Self-questioning

867
01:00:10,096 --> 01:00:11,296
勝つか負けるか
Will I win or will I lose?

868
01:00:11,296 --> 01:00:12,396
ドローなんてないわ
There's no such thing as a draw

869
01:00:12,446 --> 01:00:13,446
幕開けるわ
The curtain is rising

870
01:00:13,546 --> 01:00:14,996
カッチンして ラッキーマニー
Click it and make some lucky money

871
01:00:15,096 --> 01:00:16,696
どっちもむりー…
Both are impossible, huh?

872
01:00:17,396 --> 01:00:18,296
Cigar Cigar

873
01:00:18,596 --> 01:00:20,296
引けるか否か 自分次第だな
Can I pull it off or not? It's up to me

874
01:00:20,496 --> 01:00:22,496
余裕で！ 振り切り全BETだぜいイェイ☆
Easy! Full swing, going all in, yeah!

875
01:00:22,546 --> 01:00:23,176
そこどけ！
Get out of the way!

